23:
Whoever denies the Son does not have the 
Father either; 
he who acknowledges the Son has the Father also.

7:
For there are three that bear witness in heaven: the Father, 
the Word, and the Holy Spirit; 
and these three are one.

9:
If we receive 
the witness of men, the witness of God is greater; 
for this is the witness of God which He has testified of His Son.
